room_title: Escape room "The Warehouse of Jack Travis" by Clue Pursuit in Springfield (MO)
review: We loved this room! Jack Travis was a blast and we escaped with 8 minutes left. Will definitely go back.

room_title: Escape room "The Warehouse of Jack Travis" by Clue Pursuit in Springfield (MO)
review: My family escaped the Jack Travis room with a little help from our wonderful game master Niki! We can't wait to go back, what a fun way to spend an hour. (Well, 54 minutes to be exact...)
